'''Andrey Diyev''' ({{lang-ru|<U+0410><U+043D><U+0434><U+0440><U+0435><U+0301><U+0439> <U+0414><U+0438><U+0301><U+0435><U+0432>}}; born in 1958 in [[Minsk]], [[Byelorussian SSR]], [[Soviet Union]]) is a [[Russians|Russian]] [[pianist]].

He was trained at the [[Moscow Conservatory]], graduating under [[Lev Naumov]]. Diyev won 4th prize at the 1978 Santander [[Paloma O'Shea International Piano Competition]], and has performed and taught internationally.

Diyev has been distinguished as a Merited Artist of the Russian Federation.

